The '''Nonsentient Creatures Transportation Act''' was a law passed by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] that illegalized transporting [[Sentience/Legends|non-sentient]] creatures between [[Planet/Legends|planets]] and [[Star system/Legends|star systems]].

